# Reproducibility Guide

This document provides complete instructions for reproducing all experimental results reported in the paper. Every number in Tables 4–7 and Figures 4–8 can be reproduced using the steps below.

---

## Reproducibility Checklist

| Claim | Reproducing Script | Expected Output |
|-------|-------------------|-----------------|
| Table 4 (3-scale CloudSim) | `experiments/evaluate.py` with `--all_baselines` | `results/cloudsim/*/evaluation.json` |
| Table 5 (Kubernetes results) | `experiments/evaluate.py --config configs/kubernetes.yaml` | `results/kubernetes/evaluation.json` |
| Table 6 (Ablation study) | `experiments/ablation_study.py` | `results/ablation/ablation_summary.json` |
| Table 7 (Statistical tests) | `experiments/evaluate.py --statistics` | `results/*/statistics.json` |
| Figure 4 (Scaling curves) | `src/utils/visualization.py --plot scaling` | `results/figures/fig4_scaling.pdf` |
| Figure 5 (SHAP + ablation) | `src/utils/visualization.py --plot shap` | `results/figures/fig5_shap.pdf` |
| Figure 6 (Sensitivity) | `experiments/sensitivity_analysis.py` | `results/figures/fig6_sensitivity.pdf` |
| Figure 7 (Convergence) | `experiments/convergence_analysis.py` | `results/figures/fig7_convergence.pdf` |
| Figure 8 (LSTM-AE) | `experiments/evaluate.py --lstm_eval` | `results/figures/fig8_lstm.pdf` |

