## Random Seeds

All experiments use seeds **42 through 51** (10 independent runs). This produces the mean ± std values reported in all tables.

| Seed | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| 42 | Primary seed (used for ablation figures) |
| 43–51 | Independent replication runs |

Seeds are fixed for: NumPy, PyTorch, Python `random`, and the CloudSim environment. See `src/utils/seeds.py`:

```python
set_all_seeds(seed)   # fixes all four sources
```

