## Troubleshooting

**CUDA out of memory during 500 VM training:**
Reduce `ppo_n_steps` in `configs/cloudsim_500vm.yaml` from 2048 to 1024. Results may differ by < 0.5%.

**Google Cluster download fails:**
The `gsutil` CLI requires a Google Cloud account. The preprocessed Parquet files (post-normalization) are available as a direct download via Zenodo (see `scripts/download_datasets.sh --dataset google_cluster_preprocessed`).

**CloudSim Java dependency missing:**
```bash
sudo apt-get install default-jdk-headless
# Verify: java -version  (should show 11+)
```
